        <updateDate>2022-02-07T20:22:19Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Transparency in COVID-19 Research Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Health and Human Services (HHS) to publish, within 14 days of the bill's enactment, all the COVID-19 studies it carried out and their related findings. In publishing this information, HHS must maintain the privacy of study participants.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
